{"pageProps":{"metadata":{"title":"Flet-後期","curriculumId":"1ada501e-f337-8139-9efd-dbc938d445fb","category":"後期","visibility":["基礎班","発展班"],"tags":["基礎班","Python","Flet","GUI"],"is_basic_curriculum":true,"id":"122"},"mdBlocks":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-812b-a696-c9674bfc1b79","type":"paragraph","parent":"Fletの要素であるコントロールは自分でカスタムすることが可能です。今回は「カスタムコントロール」を紹介します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8180-8043-ee10584682af","type":"heading_2","parent":"## カストムコントロールとは","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8142-82fa-e7be49821d1c","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81f7-b298-f43fc2185e31","type":"paragraph","parent":"カスタムコントロールは、Fletにあるコントロールのクラスを継承した新たなクラスを作り、親クラスの属性の値をカスタムしたコントロールです。（クラスの継承については「[**クラスの継承**](/posts/curriculums/1ada501e-f337-81d0-93c4-cc25006a2031/1ada501e-f337-8139-983b-df7225049e88)」をご覧ください）","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8131-a1ea-c07980f4197c","type":"paragraph","parent":"例えば、見た目を変更した文字を使い回したいとします。文字を表示するには`Text`コントロールを使いますが、その見た目を変更するには`style`属性を設定しなければいけませんね。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81aa-a695-cf937c58ba31","type":"code","parent":"```python\nft.Text(\"文字\", style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))\n```","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81f3-8941-f9d5d19358d8","type":"paragraph","parent":"`Text`コントロールの`style`属性の値を何度も書くのは面倒です。`style`属性の値が事前に決まっていれば書く必要はなくなります。それを可能にするのがカスタムコントロールです。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-813e-9a0f-f9e2070ba50f","type":"heading_2","parent":"## カストムコントロールを作る","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81dc-9fd0-f0a1aef6afa9","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b2-a815-fbf38b6c4c09","type":"paragraph","parent":"それでは、カスタムコントロールを作ってみましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8186-b859-f3ff86ef438b","type":"paragraph","parent":"試しに、以下の設定のカスタムコントロールを作ってみましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8132-9564-fbace46d6ae3","type":"code","parent":"```python\nft.Text(\"文字\", style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))\n```","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-815c-929c-e63e6e656b41","type":"callout","parent":"> カスタムコントロールを作る  \n> ```python  \n> import flet as ft  \n>   \n> class CustomText(ft.Text):  \n> \tdef __init__(self,value):  \n> \t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20)  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81c8-871f-f3f550e2197e","type":"code","parent":"```python\nimport flet as ft\n\nclass CustomText(ft.Text):\n\tdef __init__(self,value):\n\t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20)\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81ec-a593-d2e0205660df","type":"paragraph","parent":"ここでは`CustomText`というカスタムコントロールを定義しました。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81d1-bbea-f2efb300cb9b","type":"paragraph","parent":"`CustomText`は、`Text`コントロールをカスタムしたコントロールであり、最初から`style`が設定されています。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-813f-9726-c36e6d943102","type":"paragraph","parent":"さっそく`CustomText`を使ってみましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8182-b4c8-cf772ab7e91f","type":"callout","parent":"> `CustomText`を使う  \n> ```python  \n> import flet as ft  \n>   \n> class CustomText(ft.Text):  \n> \tdef __init__(self,value):  \n> \t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))  \n> \t\t  \n> def main(page: ft.Page):  \n>   \n> \tnormalText = ft.Text(value=\"普通のTextコントロール\")  \n> \tcustomText = CustomText(value=\"カスタムしたTextコントロール\")  \n>   \n> \tpage.add(normalText, customText)  \n>   \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-814f-939d-d4628eee9527","type":"code","parent":"```python\nimport flet as ft\n\nclass CustomText(ft.Text):\n\tdef __init__(self,value):\n\t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))\n\t\t\ndef main(page: ft.Page):\n\n\tnormalText = ft.Text(value=\"普通のTextコントロール\")\n\tcustomText = CustomText(value=\"カスタムしたTextコントロール\")\n\n\tpage.add(normalText, customText)\n\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81a7-9825-cbeb7698219a","type":"paragraph","parent":"これを実行すると以下のような出力結果になります。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81c7-bed3-d2ca4eae10a5","type":"callout","parent":"> 実行結果  \n> ![%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88_2024-11-21_13.46.28.png](https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/4faae8b3-4c31-46a7-898b-465eb6114fd9/ce1253ca-6af5-47b3-b0a5-6a39a865800c/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88_2024-11-21_13.46.28.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466WKMHO65K%2F20250315%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20250315T021449Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjELH%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIBivcVf0eeBPk3D%2BBjvHY7rDR3bC1u3d1NKMuNkOrWK7AiBupcFwGgjTxXalcn%2FIHUWaIjmv2j9Hv3rFF5emsHrA0SqIBAj6%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAAaDDYzNzQyMzE4MzgwNSIM7AKzQe18J3p6Ct%2FvKtwDa17DwTX1c%2FufhwVaVAXIXEOQXTdq5DCZzb5yzBjEHy%2FxP0AUj%2B4TEC21HuNV9NTlSpmlpB9fVl6PHUu8LayTXrH3o%2BwnKDS%2F0LFviiNmojoOyYawcr1A93345Ufv76O3qQnLZywY1QZCJpbZWhY5HzIDpBQ5Id73pAAVlrb%2FAsIZHwT0HQ%2BTgVbEYRbNtiL9Lkoc3qRU9t6e7zBg%2B2IsI5cOpX4neJTEkdg1bPFx%2FGZ09nK8dyY5VQ6vMIoeXV1VPmh6o9gVPNt9GLZUhEGxim%2BjlO%2F2fcAWm%2B%2FYCSolDzYmox8Q0lwr%2F7RYQKVq330LUBpBo%2B4F5BktPxEydY7%2F2C4hFVuPyaDq3JjkeQKuRaxWiJzsDU1LCJKrYwxNh2S1U6NuWW3%2BvT9PYWOI8crqvHf3rU50uQ9ZgDgpwVUM1ogfDDRvE4gkBAnr6gFhlRrgQksFu7pa74i7FGWGXKIigswCSRwuwnsEuiYxaRVjRLMValGaliGqG%2FUmD9UB2SnRFS%2FfSR%2FPrSH1oLHLe2XmI%2FsruCzg2Tcp7Oc45hdsMN5RV7O0g9a2aGYX%2BxXaBoLr80zqQx9HQZknZ1tpf23U6yZTGcxv4kjmAhffHXrmaGSyrDh7vwHeJCf1ojMwz6nTvgY6pgGRWUA3GozoLvZs38VwZdTIhCj9VUWlxR%2FSoNYgkPcM7edou2%2BdCG0PQ4iGSFzBl1qWOum4Uj%2Bz%2B6cCELu9mzNIvAAEznGZeq5dHazF0e%2FMv8TSFjXWg6bQT5298VXgHO4pU9jbuwZZ6P2yXk4J6lyr8MB%2Fj%2FLGGyHiuPbgods84ZHUCYocZrnR1FN8Dgdmi1T5fSbEnwrpKlGQXQ8D8MsQetrsnzks&X-Amz-Signature=1eb51a49cc0e13ad755371be0a9fc6b9dffed7ea6a89d6e150f06e5464d97bad&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-id=GetObject)","children":[{"blockId":"1ada